sources.title: Ape Vs Monster | Full Movie | Action Adventure | Creature Feature | EXCLUSIVE
sources.description:
*Ape Vs Monster* - An ape, lost in space, crash-lands back to Earth. The vessel  oozes a sludge that triggers massive growth in both the ape, as well as a passing Gila monster. Once the creatures reach titanic size, their paths cross again, leading to a giant brawl in which Mankind hangs in the balance.
2021.  Stars: Eric Roberts, Arianna Renee, Katie Sereika
